title: Podcast Episode 54.2 – MAFIA CINDERELLA by Skye Warren
description:
Our audiobook this week is MAFIA CINDERELLA by New York Times Bestselling Author Skye Warren! 

Narrated by Lauren Sweet

One dress. One dance. Lucia has one chance to change her life—and the lives of her family. But Sebastian Conti is no prince charming. He's a dangerous man. When the clock strikes midnight, he'll determine her fate.

OVERTURE by Skye Warren: https://amzn.to/2WPQLWj

THE PAWN by Skye Warren: https://amzn.to/2qxrYtM
